{"tid":178978,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"回帶：深水埗女報販霞姐單野","createTime":"2017-03-30T02:05:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T02:05:00.000Z","uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6084ef3b4c998a142b690edf85cfd9495d765282","tid":178978,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T02:05:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20150612/19181542\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20150612%2F19181542&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfIsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=4e1c5a6a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20150612%2F19181542&h=fccb9a70\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20150612/19181542</a><br />\n<br />\n本報訊】深水埗女報販何慧霞（霞姐）於1999年反對《東方日報》發行商強迫報販增加訂紙後，招來殺身之禍。3名刀手入罪後，頂證案中主腦發行商老闆及其下屬是幕後黑手，令兩人謀殺罪成。兩人不服判決上訴，主腦更找來4名謀殺犯，力證刀手誣陷他們。上訴庭3位法官昨一致駁回兩人上訴，更指主腦找來極度暴戾的謀殺犯作證，是弄巧反拙。<br />\n記者：梁偉強<br />\n<br />\n----<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一定係蘋果老屈東方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}